Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep your poker face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking my father's teaching to heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle magician glides amidst the skycraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's target is the Dark Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears of Love for The Dark Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief is definitely hiding in the vicinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving him a pair of steel bracelets today!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The forecast said it would rain…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know it would rain so much I couldn't use my hang glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in trouble, Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um…who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying he let The Kid get away, Superintendent Chaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, an email was sent to Section Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It said, "This time, I'll welcome The Kid as my accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This coming Friday, enjoy the nightmare put on\Nby the two of us at Shuho Museum"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a criminal planner in a strange mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who works with thieves from all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and takes half of the cut for helping them\Nin their break in and getaway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's got a 100% success rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would the Kid work with a person like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who's worked with Nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are released from all the nightmares in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and achieve more happiness than they could hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they say among the criminals of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure The Kid was drawn to that happiness\Nor whatever that he promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamori, you will finally be released from\Nthe nightmare of The Kid as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually…this is still undisclosed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone who's successfully worked with Nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is arrested before the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or shot down by the local police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With the gift of half the treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and "death," rather than happiness, in their hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? I want to arrest The Kid alive…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But this matter is not only in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With a red arrest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Red arrest order…you mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,An international arrest order seeking physical custody\Nof fugitives for extradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigators from ICPO,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpol is coming with one of those in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,136 men in front,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,103 in back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,185 inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,47 on the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,6 helicopters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,all men in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Standby until time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't neglect your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Interpol see you yawning or anything!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Interpol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakamori, the man in charge here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it's you, Kaito…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah…you called me here so I came…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to have a look at our security system,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're so good at magic tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably ask a famous magician instead of me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a top level magician yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,your father trained you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if the world found out that the police begged\Na magician for help because of The Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that would just look really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that suits me just fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind hearing all the tricks before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoko!? Why are you dressed like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told one of the riot police
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that I always wanted to try wearing one of these,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and they lent me an extra one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this security alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show him too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but my father's really trying hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so I couldn't have him come all the way here…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you fighting the bad guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I'll get him and smash him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil will never flourish in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you're on my Papa's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa…who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kenta Connery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My Papa's been chasing this bad guy named Nightmare for a real long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,he's an important guy at this place called Interpol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jack Connery from Interpol
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My men are waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only cooperate with you, the local police,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have the power to make any arrests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Japanese is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife is Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Though she passed away three years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenta!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh, my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were coming back to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so I hid in the bathroom of this museum from last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Security's full of holes after all…this should be a piece of cake…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everyone must be worried about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I was going to stay in your hotel with you, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to bring him back…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What, I have to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my daughter, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have her bring the lunches and other things…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She got changed fast…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To the child care facility that's taking care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to travel all over the world for my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and after losing my wife, I wasn't able to look after him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can I take you up on your offer and have you take him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Connery, your men on standby are calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll leave Nightmare to you, Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll arrest The Kid and anyone who's with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we both want to get rid of the weights
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been carrying on our shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just one thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In your honest opinion, what kind of man is Nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the words of a thief who worked with him and lived to tell the tale,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare gets into a person's soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,sees right through it, and controls it at will,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he is truly the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil that controls a person's soul…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The escape route I chose for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you do live up to your name
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,as the crime planner with a 100% success rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you know who I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This coming Friday…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up! I'm sorry, but I'm not working with you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you're going to play it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You act like a lone wolf…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man who sometimes pretends to be you,\Nand helps you in your escape…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I love magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a world famous magician I was a fan of, left this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and The Kid disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that magician was The Kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but eight years on, seeing him return,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suspicious of his assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's older, and he can't carry it out alone..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jii…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came up with a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He found a new master,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and had him begin working as the second Kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story, or information the police would appreciate…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Resistance is futile,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you are always under my control…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the black opal earrings Nightmare and The Kid are after,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the Dark Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't check if it's got the Pandora in it or not without\Nholding it up to the moonlight…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've got a security system in place developed\Nto stop The Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To open the lid of the hard glass case, you have to\Ntake off the chains
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that have high voltage electricity running through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple, but impregnable, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the case is held up in the air to keep the\Ncase itself from sinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd get it, Kaito! I'm glad I asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The liquid inside the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you're going to put the earrings\Non the stand in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Black opals need moisture, that's where I got the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Curator Kondo!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he can't fight on an empty stomach, and\Nwent to get dinner…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At an important time like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside is 48cm all around, the inside has a\Ndiameter of 16cm…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think of this system, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he won't be able to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless he's able to open the lid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're still here, Aoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's leave this to your Papa and my father…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm going to fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the bad guy with Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be just like Papa…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine…I've got medicine…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are painkillers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said something bad is living inside of my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I must have surgery to fix the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery…what…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! Papa told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When Nightmare's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be able to get rid of the wild horses in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I can live with him all the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we get some curry rice at a family restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat your carrots, the wild horses in your head\Nmight settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of horses…did you see him inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this "him" you keep talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. I got a text telling me to tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's looking forward to seeing you here…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you mean…could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this fine, Saguru…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's some villain with a scary name involved tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about that, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Nightmare's symbol is a black horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The black horse in chess is the knight, who plays second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means I, Saguru Hakuba, the white knight\Nwho makes the first move…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,(P.S. Hakuba literally means white horse)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Has to stand on the board for the game to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Six helicopters on the lookout in the skies…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,472 riot police in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With radio interception and security system hacking…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say I know everything about the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd usually tell you how to break in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and guide you out through the escape route I've selected,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I suppose you don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll go get it, just sleep tight until then…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, Curator Kondo is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Curator!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only 30 minutes left until The Kid's scheduled appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, and what is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to place the jewels in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do a final check of the case, just in case…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something floating in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably some dust from when we placed the chains on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, you're probably right, everything looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, place the jewels on the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, put the lid on…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Woops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! Must be my age…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, put the chains on and hang it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph…everything's going well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need Hakuba to fall for the trick I played…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry…Saguru…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so close…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose this street, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When we stopped at the gas station just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an emergency text from Inspector Nakamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I immediately called him back on the number he sent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,he told me this way was faster…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent you on this crowded street on purpose to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…your grandmother was too stupid…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know he doesn't want me there before\Nhe commits the crime…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll run over on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Saguru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Nakamori…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori! This is Saguru Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuba!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, what is the situation over there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation…nothing's happened yet…huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this room a little too dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just put the lights down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Opals are 6 to 10% water,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and can crack when they become too dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so they shouldn't be kept under bright lights
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have heard about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this is too…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…you're right…it's almost as if
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we're asking for the opals to be stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the back up power on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The jewels!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, they're right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're floating in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Opals have a specific gravity of 2.10 to 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't possibly float in water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you saying they're fakes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll authenticate them…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,take them off the chain and take the lid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait! Don't touch anything until I get there…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,These…are fakes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little, Kid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Connery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just been informed that the jewels were stolen by The Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you couldn't stop him after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We know The Nightmare's habits, and he's working with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All men, follow orders and act immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Close in on both men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver, follow that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That someone at my facility found a good doctor\Nthat can fix my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So he doesn't have to worry about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he can just focus on fighting the bad guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,please just let me tell him that, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kid had already switched the jewels out before the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He then put the lights out and knocked the case over
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and dropped the jewels into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to show us they were fakes and laugh at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,…That's strange
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange? What is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A case filled this high with water
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,would normally leave a higher water mark when tilted over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But this case only has a water mark up to the edges…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which means it was barely tilted over, and the water barely moved…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A transparent acrylic sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He placed small stoppers on the four corners of the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,sank the acrylic sheet up to the stoppers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the water level shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shallow enough that it looked like the jewels were floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Then the jewels…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Were of course real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Curator Kondo was put asleep in the bathroom…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's The Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kid was disguised as the Curator and took the jewels,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Dark Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency deployment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already out of his disguise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and flying through the air on his white wings…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to choose you, Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Great happiness will surely now come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? We're supposed to split the spoils…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but those aren't the jewels I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These aren't the ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't contain the stone of life, Pandora,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that the organization that killed my father are after…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Often returns the jewels he went through the trouble of stealing…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as my research said you'd act…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else you heard directly from the Japanese police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpol's Jack Connery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it by hacking into the security system
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and intercepting wireless communications…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you get the numbers wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There were 136 riot police in front,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,103 in back,185 inside, and 47 on the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for a total of 471!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You counted one extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you counted that girl messing around in a riot police uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't through hacking or intercepting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You counted them yourself when you were there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm going around to different countries,\Nit happens sometimes…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of rivalry or pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,local police will deliberately give me wrong information…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why I always go and count the number of men myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with my own eyes, but I guess that backfired on me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so when your partner uncovers your identity, you kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I always work with a thief making trouble for that country,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they take the credit and say I didn't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems my men, who know nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,are following orders and bringing the local police here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To pick up the body of the foolish thief with\Nhalf the treasure in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange that this foolish thief came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,while knowing who you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When Nightmare's gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be able to get rid of the wild horses in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I can live with him all the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could save up enough for your son's expensive surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll stop being Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what that meant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenta…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get much for whatever you steal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you took it all for yourself, nobody would work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop where you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kenta's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way here to tell me that…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to, after hearing him say that…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be just like my Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No…I can't, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep showing thieves nightmares!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing this mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Papaaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kenta!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, he…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let…it go…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let those jewels go, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't…these will pay for…pay for Kenta's surgery…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Papaaaaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be just like my Papa…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Papa! Papaaaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have fallen, protecting the jewels!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that The Kid tried to save him…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Nightmare's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, The Kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So he left his partner and fled, leaving the jewels behind…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole the nightmare from this boy known as truth...
